query:
SELECT a.code, count(*) QTY
FROM
                ILM.CODE_LABEL_LOG@PROD_MX.MAT.AVAGOTECH.NET a
WHERE
                a.DEVICE like '1%'
  AND a.PRINT_DATE = (select max(print_date) from ilm.code_label_log@PROD_MX.MAT.AVAGOTECH.NET where device = a.device)
  AND a.PRINT_DATE > to_date('20151128 063000','YYYYMMDD HH24MISS')
  AND a.PRINT_DATE <= to_date('20151129 063000','YYYYMMDD HH24MISS')
  and (a.code like '%PIC-10410%')
GROUP BY a.CODE
